Jena Engstrom https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jena_Engstrom 0 Jena Engstrom (born Liana Jeanne Moon on June 30, 1942 in Los Angeles, California) is an American former television actress. She appeared in more than three dozen episodes of various television series between 1960 and 1964.
